# Speckit Plan Workflow

Use this workflow to create a technical implementation plan.

## Steps

1. Create or update `openspec/specs/implementation_plan.md`:

```markdown
# Implementation Plan

## Overview
[Brief description of what will be built]

## Tech Stack
- Language: [e.g., Python 3.9+]
- Framework: [e.g., Typer + Rich]
- Testing: [e.g., Pytest]

## Components

### Component 1: [Name]
- Files: `path/to/file.py`
- Changes: [Description]

### Component 2: [Name]
- Files: `path/to/file.py`  
- Changes: [Description]

## Dependencies
- [Dependency 1]
- [Dependency 2]

## Verification
- [ ] Unit tests pass
- [ ] Integration tests pass
- [ ] Manual testing complete
```

2. Review plan against requirements

3. Get approval before implementation
